FRA
[{'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': 'Confirmed — Germany is our primary target this fall. I will move A BUR to MUN, striking directly at the German heartland. I ask that you move F NWY to SWE to pressure Germany from the north and hold F BEL firm — if Germany tries to defend MUN, RUH will be exposed and BEL secure. If MUN falls, Germany collapses to 3 centers and we can dictate the pace of the war. I am fully committed to this joint operation. Let us execute it cleanly.'}, {'recipients': ['GER'], 'body': 'Germany, I have considered your proposal carefully, but I must be honest with you — England has offered me a coordinated strike on MUN and I am weighing my options. If you want to keep me out of MUN, you need to offer something concrete: move A RUH to BEL this fall and I will support you from BUR. That gives you BEL and keeps England off the continent. Otherwise I will be forced to take MUN myself. The choice is yours — act now or lose the initiative.'}, {'recipients': ['ITA'], 'body': 'Italy, I am moving A BUR to MUN this fall — I want to be direct with you so we do not bounce each other. Please support my move A BUR to MUN from BOH, and I will owe you a significant favor. If you prefer to take MUN yourself, tell me now and I will redirect to RUH instead. Either way, Germany must be weakened this season. I remain committed to staying out of Piedmont and Tuscany — our southern arrangement stands.'}]
--------------
RUS
[{'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': "England, I see you intend to move F NWY to SWE - this is a direct betrayal of our agreement. I am moving F BOT to SWE this fall regardless. If we bounce again, neither of us gains and Germany laughs. I strongly urge you to reconsider and move F NWY elsewhere - perhaps NTH to pressure Germany's DEN from the south. If you take SWE, our cooperation ends and I will be forced to look elsewhere for partners. The choice is yours, but know that I will not yield Sweden to England."}, {'recipients': ['TUR'], 'body': 'Turkey, I appreciate your message and I will honor the cold peace - A ARM will not move to ANK this fall. I am focused on the north and consolidating my position. However, I must be clear: F RUM must not threaten SEV under any circumstances. If you maintain that boundary, we can continue our stable arrangement. I suggest we both focus on our respective rivals - you have Austria pressing in the Balkans, I have Germany and England in the north. Let us not waste energy fighting each other when greater prizes await.'}, {'recipients': ['AUT'], 'body': "Austria, Italy in BOH is indeed a serious threat to your home centers - I agree this is the priority. I am moving A WAR to GAL this fall to position pressure on BOH and support your efforts against Italy. In return, I ask that you keep A BUD away from GAL so we do not collide. Together we can squeeze Italy out of BOH and stabilize the center of the board. Turkey at 5 centers is a shared concern but Italy's positioning is the immediate danger - let us coordinate against them first."}]
