[{'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': "Confirmed — A BUR moves to MUN this season. Hold BEL firm and keep F HOL in place to pin German armies. If MUN falls, Germany is broken and we divide the north between us. I take MUN and we coordinate next season on the remaining German centers. This is the moment — let's execute."}, {'recipients': ['ITA'], 'body': 'Final confirmation: I am moving A BUR to MUN this season. If you support from BOH, MUN falls and Germany is finished. You gain a free hand against Austria with no German interference, and I owe you a favor. This is the decisive blow — A BOH supports A BUR into MUN. Do it and we both profit enormously.'}, {'recipients': ['GER'], 'body': "I have held off England's pressure as long as I can. You gave me nothing — no move to BEL, no concrete gesture. I warned you this moment would come. The fault lies with your inaction, not my ambition. France must expand or perish — that is the nature of this game."}]
