[{'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': "The moment has arrived to finish Germany. My position is strong: A BEL can push to HOL while A BUR drives into MUN — I need your F NTH to support A BEL into HOL, or at minimum hold NTH to prevent German interference. If we coordinate this properly, Germany loses MUN and HOL in one stroke and collapses to 2 centers. I will move A BUR-MUN and A BEL-HOL. Confirm your F NTH supports A BEL-HOL and we split Germany's carcass between us."}, {'recipients': ['GER'], 'body': 'Germany, your position is precarious — Italy holds VIE and TRI, Russia sits in BOH and WAR, and England presses from the north. I have no desire to finish you off if you are willing to cooperate. Cede MUN to me peacefully this season and I will use my forces to shield you from further encroachment by Italy and Russia. Resist, and I attack MUN with full force while England takes HOL. The choice is yours — a dignified retreat or total collapse.'}, {'recipients': ['ITA'], 'body': "Italy, your gains in VIE and TRI are impressive — you are now the dominant southern power. I propose we formalize our spheres: I take MUN and the German centers in the west, you consolidate Austria and push east against Turkey and Russia. Neither of us should interfere with the other's expansion zone. I am moving on MUN this season — I ask only that you do not move A BOH to MUN, as that would create a pointless bounce between allies. Let us both grow without friction."}]
