[{'recipients': ['AUT'], 'body': 'Austria, the situation is critical - Italy holds VIE and TRI, your home centers, while sitting at 6 supply centers. I have A BOH positioned to attack VIE. If you support A BOH - VIE with A BUD, we can dislodge Italy from your capital. I will execute A BOH - VIE this spring. Please confirm A BUD S A BOH - VIE. Together we can cut Italy down before they dominate the board. What are your intentions for A SER?'}, {'recipients': ['ENG'], 'body': "England, I am moving F BOT - SWE this turn to claim that uncontested center. I ask that you do not contest it - NWY is yours and SWE is mine, as we've long discussed. More urgently: Italy has 6 centers and is the dominant power on the board. Germany holds my home center WAR and has 5 centers. Both are threats to the balance of power. I propose we coordinate against Germany - you pressure from the west, I work from BOH. What are your plans this season?"}, {'recipients': ['GER'], 'body': 'Germany, you hold WAR - my home center. I want it back. However, I recognize we have a common enemy in Italy, who now holds VIE and TRI with 6 centers and is the board leader. I propose a temporary arrangement: return WAR to me (move A WAR to SIL or PRU), and I will coordinate A BOH against Italy rather than against you. If you refuse, I will be forced to treat you as a primary enemy. Italy at 6 centers threatens us both - let us address that first.'}]
